.DT
npc_shout_event
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
npc_shout_event

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
npc_shout_event -  This method is called by the shout command to filter the shouts onto the npcs that are listening.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void npc_shout_event(object shouter,
string start,
string message,
string lang,
int * coord,
int range)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^shouter%^RESET%^ - the person who shouted
%^BOLD%^start%^RESET%^ - the start of the message
%^BOLD%^message%^RESET%^ - the message shouted
%^BOLD%^lang%^RESET%^ - the language the message is in
%^BOLD%^coord%^RESET%^ - the co-ordinate it was shouted from
%^BOLD%^range%^RESET%^ - the range of the shout

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/broadcaster.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is called by the shout command to filter the shouts onto
the npcs that are listening.
.EP

